import { Box, Button, Card, CardMedia, Stack } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'
import image from '../image/IMG_4214.JPG'

const CardProduct = () => {
  return (
    <Stack width={200} spacing={2}>

      <CardMedia
        component="img"
        alt="green iguana"
        height="140"
        image={image}
      />
      <Button variant="contained">retail(ขายปลีก)</Button>
      <Button variant="contained">wholesale(ขายส่ง)</Button>
    </Stack>
  )
}

export default CardProduct
